248
00:18:35,160 --> 00:18:36,679
Pero may trabaho na ako sa Lan City.

249
00:18:36,680 --> 00:18:37,680
Alam ko.

250
00:18:38,039 --> 00:18:39,319
Ang ibig kong sabihin ay,

251
